content.rendered:
Four years after the island of Nublar was destroyed, dinosaurs are now living – and hunting – among humans around the world. This fragile balance will reshape the future and determine once and for all whether human beings will remain the top predators on the planet they must now share with the most fearsome creatures in history.

Directed By Colin Trevorrow

Written By Emily Carmichael. Colin Trevorrow. Derek Connolly

Stars: Chris Pratt. Bryce Dallas Howard. Laura Dern
